      <title>佳兆业、时代中国在香港面临法院诉讼以避免被清算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/chinese-builder-kaisa-faces-key-court-test-to-avoid-liquidation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国开发商佳兆业集团控股有限公司和时代中国控股有限公司将于周一与债权人展开对峙，寻求避免在香港法庭接受清算。目前，不利于该行业的判决已开始堆积如山。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/chinese-builder-kaisa-faces-key-court-test-to-avoid-liquidation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 07:27:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
